note: expected this to be `User`
   --> crates/db/some-sqlite/examples/demo.rs:43:8
    |
43  | struct NewUser {
    |        ^^^^^^^
note: required by a bound in `create`

152 |     async fn create<N>(&self, entity: N) -> Result<E>
    |              ------ required by a bound in this associated function
153 |     where
154 |         N: NewEntity<Entity = E> + Serialize + Send;
    |                      ^^^^^^^^^^ required by this bound in `Repository::create`
